    "text": "Rural Opportunity Zone and Investment Act \n\nThis bill provides for the deferral of tax until December 31, 2032, on capital gains invested in qualified rural opportunity zones. A qualified rural opportunity zone is any population census tract that is located in a rural county and is in persistent poverty."
